Creating mural for your child's bedroom is
a long and complicated process but well worth

00:00:04.900 --> 00:00:09.211
the effort. As long as you make sure you have
the necessary supplies on hand. You want to

00:00:09.211 --> 00:00:12.300
make sure you have everything you need so
you don't have start and stop and go all the

00:00:12.300 --> 00:00:16.909
time and that you're able to do a great product.
First, we're going to need to have a variety

00:00:16.909 --> 00:00:22.509
of rollers. I recommend having two small rollers
two large rollers so that then you can alter

00:00:22.509 --> 00:00:25.119
if you're using them in a different paint
colors. You don't have to wait to wash them

00:00:25.119 --> 00:00:30.960
and dry them. Also of course, need painting
trays at least two of these. Again the same

00:00:30.960 --> 00:00:35.660
reason with the rollers so that you can be
working with multiple colors at the same time.

00:00:35.660 --> 00:00:41.760
Also a good flat head screwdriver really great
for opening up paint cans. A variety of brushes

00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:46.440
big just typical painting brushes nothing
special about these guys just yet some nice

