have and also to again add some of the painting

00:01:10.319 --> 00:01:18.340
effects we're going to do today. Some good
painting tape to cover up those surfaces a

00:01:18.340 --> 00:01:23.569
good strong sharp pencil so make sure you
also have your pencil sharper on hand. Now,

